        = = Rune3DS = =

Rune3DS is a minimal 3DS on-device catalog client.
It is licensed under GPLv3. See LICENSE for details.

      = = Building = =

Requirements:
 - mbedtls, bundled through nnc
 - bannertool
 - makerom
 - perl
 - devkitARM
 - libctru
 - citro2d
 - citro3d

Run this for a release build:

 ./build.pl --target release

The release CIA is built as Rune3DS.cia.

Configuration can be set as environment variables or through --configure.

Common build variables:
 - targets,TARGETS=targets-list
 - debug,DEBUG=1
 - release,RELEASE=1
 - http_backend,HTTP_BACKEND=backend
 - full_log,FULL_LOG=1
 - device_id,DEVICE_ID=device-id-int
 - debug_server,HS_DEBUG_SERVER="debug-server"
 - update_base,HS_UPDATE_BASE="update-url"
 - rune_update_base,RUNE_UPDATE_BASE="rune-update-url"
 - nb_base,HS_NB_BASE="nbapi-url"
 - cdn_base,HS_CDN_BASE="cdn-url"
 - site_url,HS_SITE_URL="site-url"

You also need a local source/hsapi_auth.c. That file is ignored by Git and
must not be committed.

    = = Development = =

Rune3DS is written in C and C++, with Perl and shell scripts for build tooling.
Important directories:

  3hstool/               theme build tool
  3rd/                   third-party code
  cia_stuff/             CIA metadata and assets
  source/, include/      source code
  data/, romfs/          runtime files
  gfx/                   built-in graphics
  lang/                  translation files
